  "instructions": [
    "Heat a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add 1 tsp of oil and swirl to coat the pan.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the mustard, dijon mustard, sugar, and dill. Cook for 1 minute, until the sugar dissolves.",
    "Add the lemon juice and cook for another minute, until the mixture is slightly thickened.",
    "Add the smoked salmon and break it up with a spatula.",
    "Add the fried rice and stir-fry until the rice is well combined with the other ingredients.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the pilaf to a serving dish and serve immediately.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh dill if desired."
